程序包 android.car.telemetry

  • 接口概要 
    接口 说明
    CarTelemetryManager.AddMetricsConfigCallback
    Application must pass a CarTelemetryManager.AddMetricsConfigCallback to use CarTelemetryManager.addMetricsConfig(String, byte[], Executor, AddMetricsConfigCallback)
    CarTelemetryManager.MetricsReportCallback
    Application must pass a CarTelemetryManager.MetricsReportCallback object to receive finished reports from CarTelemetryManager.getFinishedReport(String, Executor, MetricsReportCallback) and CarTelemetryManager.getAllFinishedReports(Executor, MetricsReportCallback).
    CarTelemetryManager.ReportReadyListener
    Application can optionally use CarTelemetryManager.setReportReadyListener(Executor, ReportReadyListener) to receive report ready notifications.
  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    CarTelemetryManager
    Provides an application interface for interacting with the Car Telemetry Service.

    CarTelemetryManager.MetricsReportStatus
